Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2013.group14.xtraveler.Control.main.commands

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    Command is an interface which concrete command will implements It is extends by an interface OpenCommand, which are Login Command, SignUp Command and so on Also it is implemented by an abstract class SessionCommand, which are SearchPlaceCommand and so on
    OpenCommand
    Command is an interface which concrete command will implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddFriend
    Able to add friend with this command for later use, can set permission for user's friend
    AddVisitedPlaceCommand
    AddVisitedPlaceCommand corresponds to add visited place button in client side
    AddWishPlaceCommand
    AddVisitedPlaceCommand corresponds to add visited place button in client side
    DeleteFriend
    Delete a friend by apply this command
    DeleteVisitedPlaceCommand
    Delete visited place by applying this command
    DeleteWishPlaceCommand
    Deletes wish place from user's wish list
    ExecutionContext
    ExecutionContext provide DAO class and session factory to the concrete command
    GetVisitedListCommand
    Lists the user's visited place
    GetWishListCommand
    Lists the user's wish place list
    ListFriend
    Lists the user's friend
    ListPlaceDetailCommand
    List the place detail of the one attraction including city name, state name, url and place feature.
    LoginCommand
    Give user access to his main page, also generate a session key for client.
    LogOutCommand
    LogOutCommand reply to the request to log out the user, and remove the session key from the sessionRegistry map.
    PersonalPageCommand
    Load the personal page for client, provide the wish list, visited list and travel plan of the user
    PlanComment
    PlanComment insert a plan comment in the databse.
    SearchPlaceCommand
    SearchPlaceCommand list the attraction of the city for the user
    SessionCommand
    SessionCommand is the super class of all commands who need session key.
    ShowCommonFeaturePlace
    List the places with the similar feature of other places.
    ShowCommonInterestUser
    List the user with similar travel interest.
    ShowCommonWishUser
    This will show us the user with similar wish travel place.
    SignUpCommand  
    UpdateUserInfo
    Update the user information.
    WritePlaceComment  
    WritePlanCommand
    WritePlanCommand is a SessionCommand's subclass, which need to be authenticated By applying this command, user can achieve writing a plan.
